title: New Mint.Club post shared with XRP, Hive, Twitter & Koinos Network telegram
body:
Hi everyone!

This post was created with the intention of exposing the Mint.Club to the XRP community, the Hive community and the Koinos Network community in order to share the benefits that I've personally seen over the last 3 months as well as the decentralized community capital benefits of easy-to-create tokens with the safety of curve-bonding.
